Kyanta Deon MAGEE No. 2017-KK-2038 Supreme Court of Louisiana. March 23, 2018 ON WRIT OF CERTIORARI TO THE COURT OF APPEAL, SECOND CIRCUIT, PARISH OF CADDO Writ denied. HUGHES, J., would grant.
